Component.Description:
A component which tethers one entity to another. The position can be adjusted, and the rotation
is relative the the owning Entity's position and the user's head position.

@param target Entity to which this owning Entity is tethered to.
@param rotateAround How many degrees to rotate around the the entity, relative to the user.
@param yawOffset After rotating around the entity, how much additional yaw to apply.
@param zOffset Z position offset.
@param yOffset Y position offset.
